| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2478 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5f73b7bb-3a88-5dda-8261-2f5dc358d6ed"
